            "descriptionRaw": "<color=#FFD780FF>Normal Attack</color>\nPerforms up to 4 water splash attacks that deal <color=#80C0FFFF>Hydro DMG</color>.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Charged Attack</color>\nConsumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal <color=#80C0FFFF>AoE Hydro DMG</color> after a short casting time.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Plunging Attack</color>\nGathering the might of Hydro, Barbara plunges towards the ground from mid-air, damaging all opponents in her path. Deals <color=#80C0FFFF>AoE Hydro DMG</color> upon impact with the ground.",
            "name": "Whisper of Water"
        },
